QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when lifecycle_rules is null then 'alarm'
    else 'ok'
  end as status,
  case
    when lifecycle_rules is null then name || ' does not have lifecycle policy.'
    else name || ' has a lifecycle policy.'
  end as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_s3_bucket;
